    • 方法详细资料

      • ignoreCase

        public PayloadTrie.PayloadTrieBuilder<T> ignoreCase()
        Configure the Trie to ignore case when searching for keywords in the text. This must be called before calling addKeyword because the algorithm converts keywords to lowercase as they are added, depending on this case sensitivity setting.
        返回:
        This builder.

      • ignoreOverlaps

        public PayloadTrie.PayloadTrieBuilder<T> ignoreOverlaps()
        Configure the Trie to ignore overlapping keywords.
        返回:
        This builder.

      • addKeyword

        public PayloadTrie.PayloadTrieBuilder<T> addKeyword(java.lang.String keyword)
        Adds a keyword to the Trie's list of text search keywords. No Payload is supplied.
        参数:
        keyword - The keyword to add to the list.
        返回:
        This builder.
        抛出:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - if the keyword is null.

      • addKeyword

                                                    T payload)

        参数:
        keyword - The keyword to add to the list.
        payload - the payload to add
        返回:
        This builder.
        抛出:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - if the keyword is null.

      • onlyWholeWordsWhiteSpaceSeparated

        public PayloadTrie.PayloadTrieBuilder<T> onlyWholeWordsWhiteSpaceSeparated()
        Configure the Trie to match whole keywords that are separated by whitespace in the text. For example, "this keyword thatkeyword" would only match the first occurrence of "keyword".
        返回:
        This builder.

      • stopOnHit

        public PayloadTrie.PayloadTrieBuilder<T> stopOnHit()

        返回:
        This builder.
